      <title>特朗普威胁后中国承诺接收非法移民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/china-promises-to-take-back-illegal-migrants-after-trump-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁对哥伦比亚征收高达 50% 的关税，以抗议该国拒绝接收被驱逐的移民。此后，中国承诺接受在美国境内的非法中国公民返回。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/china-promises-to-take-back-illegal-migrants-after-trump-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 07:55:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟将同意延长对俄罗斯的制裁，匈牙利将作出让步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/eu-set-to-agree-to-extend-russia-sanctions-hungary-to-back-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，欧盟将于周一同意延长对俄罗斯因乌克兰战争而实施的制裁，而匈牙利已准备取消对此举的反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/eu-set-to-agree-to-extend-russia-sanctions-hungary-to-back-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 07:04:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非非国大希望国家财政部拯救 Transnet</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/south-africa-s-anc-wants-national-treasury-to-rescue-transnet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非最大的政党将要求国家财政部在下个月的预算之前考虑为国有铁路和港口运营商 Transnet SOC Ltd. 提供一次性债务减免方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/south-africa-s-anc-wants-national-treasury-to-rescue-transnet</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 07:00:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南政治改革迈向二月议会投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/vietnam-political-overhaul-moves-toward-february-parliament-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南的政治体制改革方案已获共产党最高委员会的批准，其中包括合并主要部委和裁减职位，目前等待议会通过。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/vietnam-political-overhaul-moves-toward-february-parliament-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 06:19:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国间谍嫌疑人妻子否认菲律宾指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/wife-of-chinese-accused-of-spying-denies-philippines-allegation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名被指控从事间谍活动的中国公民的菲律宾妻子表示，她的丈夫不是间谍，此案发生在菲律宾和中国地缘政治紧张的背景下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/wife-of-chinese-accused-of-spying-denies-philippines-allegation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 06:18:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平的换届之年为下届领导人提供线索</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/xi-s-year-of-reshuffles-to-provide-clues-on-next-set-of-leaders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国家主席习近平的政府今年将进行一系列提拔，这将让人们首次看到新一代官员将成为国家下一届最高领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/xi-s-year-of-reshuffles-to-provide-clues-on-next-set-of-leaders</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚投资者准备应对特朗普关税导致的比索暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/colombia-investors-brace-for-peso-slump-on-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在哥伦比亚与美国就驱逐移民问题产生的争端引发了唐纳德·特朗普总统短暂的关税威胁之后，哥伦比亚交易员们正准备迎接周一的动荡交易日。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/colombia-investors-brace-for-peso-slump-on-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 22:30:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅尔茨和马斯克与德国选择党调情，德国选举禁忌被打破</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/german-election-taboos-broken-as-merz-and-musk-flirt-with-afd</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距离德国提前大选仅剩四周，随着竞选活动转向争议不断的移民问题以及埃隆·马斯克加大对极右翼德国选择党 (AfD) 的支持，政治气氛正在不断升温。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/german-election-taboos-broken-as-merz-and-musk-flirt-with-afd</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 15:49:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>洛杉矶迎来急需的降雨，但面临山体滑坡风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/los-angeles-is-getting-good-rain-yet-faces-risk-of-landslides</link>
      <description><![CDATA[干旱的洛杉矶迎来了数月来的第一场降雨——潮湿的天气有助于扑灭野火，但也带来了山体滑坡的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/los-angeles-is-getting-good-rain-yet-faces-risk-of-landslides</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 14:36:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刚果卢旺达支持的叛军称他们占领了关键城市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-26/congo-severs-ties-with-rwanda-as-rebels-close-in-on-goma-displacing-thousands</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刚果戈马（美联社）——周一凌晨，卢旺达支持的叛军声称已占领刚果东部最大城市戈马，联合国称戈马 200 万居民陷入大规模恐慌，刚果政府则称叛军的推进是“宣战”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-26/congo-severs-ties-with-rwanda-as-rebels-close-in-on-goma-displacing-thousands</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 10:26:51 GMT</pubDate>
